WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue(Default) {
color: #ffffffff;
font-family: "Arial", sans-serif;
font-size: 020px;
text-shadow: #000000ff -2px 0px 2px, #000000ff 0px 2px 2px, #000000ff 0px -2px 2px, #000000ff 2px 0px 2px;
background-color: #00000000;
}

c0000000
00:00:01.170 --> 00:00:02.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
How could this happen?</b></Default>

c0000001
00:00:04.170 --> 00:00:06.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>First, they dared
to target our Mother.</b></Default>

c0000002
00:00:06.670 --> 00:00:09.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And now they're after Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000003
00:00:09.260 --> 00:00:11.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Commendable efforts, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000004
00:00:11.090 --> 00:00:12.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?</b></Default>

c0000005
00:00:13.060 --> 00:00:16.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thank you
for protecting young Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000006
00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:18.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hello, Mother.</b></Default>

c0000007
00:00:18.440 --> 00:00:22.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I...I am by your side
once again.</b></Default>

c0000008
00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:23.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>So, I see.</b></Default>

c0000009
00:00:23.900 --> 00:00:26.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is most reassuring
to have you back here</b></Default>

c0000010
00:00:26.110 --> 00:00:27.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>where you belong.</b></Default>

c0000011
00:00:27.400 --> 00:00:29.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now then...
where's Vichyssoise?</b></Default>

c0000012
00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:32.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Captured, they're
holding her in the dungeon.</b></Default>

c0000013
00:00:32.870 --> 00:00:34.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And there's more...</b></Default>

c0000014
00:00:34.160 --> 00:00:35.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have some confidential intel.</b></Default>

c0000015
00:00:37.330 --> 00:00:39.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean that Vichyssoise
has transformed</b></Default>

c0000016
00:00:39.120 --> 00:00:41.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>into a deformed monster?</b></Default>

c0000017
00:00:41.630 --> 00:00:42.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000018
00:00:42.880 --> 00:00:45.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The House of Hydra must have
had prior knowledge of this.</b></Default>

c0000019
00:00:45.920 --> 00:00:47.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They cannot be trusted.</b></Default>

c0000020
00:00:48.010 --> 00:00:51.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yet the Hydra have wholly
denied any involvement,</b></Default>

c0000021
00:00:51.390 --> 00:00:53.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and claim that
Vichyssoise acted alone.</b></Default>

c0000022
00:00:53.760 --> 00:00:55.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They're saying
the explosion was treachery,</b></Default>

c0000023
00:00:55.970 --> 00:00:57.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>care of the House of Zoa.</b></Default>

c0000024
00:00:57.890 --> 00:01:00.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If only we had
concrete evidence.</b></Default>

c0000025
00:01:00.270 --> 00:01:03.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We can put all this nonsense
to rest once Sisbell returns.</b></Default>

c0000026
00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:04.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-When can we expect Schwartz...
-I assume you've had an</b></Default>

c0000027
00:01:05.020 --> 00:01:06.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-audience with Schwartz..
-...to return to the palace?</b></Default>

c0000028
00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:07.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Right, Mother?
-Soon, yes?</b></Default>

c0000029
00:01:07.610 --> 00:01:09.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000030
00:01:09.110 --> 00:01:11.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What happened?
He hasn't returned?</b></Default>

c0000031
00:01:11.700 --> 00:01:15.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>According to Sisbell, he should
have been here by now.</b></Default>

c0000032
00:01:15.410 --> 00:01:17.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're sure?
He's not here?</b></Default>

c0000033
00:01:17.240 --> 00:01:19.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000034
00:01:19.910 --> 00:01:21.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Greetings, Majesty.</b></Default>

c0000035
00:01:21.790 --> 00:01:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, and Alice, as well.</b></Default>

c0000036
00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:26.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[chuckles]
I looked everywhere for you.</b></Default>

c0000037
00:01:26.380 --> 00:01:28.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You should stay safe
in your chamber.</b></Default>

c0000038
00:01:28.670 --> 00:01:30.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[devious chuckle]</b></Default>

c0000039
00:01:30.470 --> 00:01:33.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Did Sisbell's servant
pay you a little visit?</b></Default>

c0000040
00:01:33.390 --> 00:01:34.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000041
00:01:34.550 --> 00:01:36.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How dare you?</b></Default>

c0000042
00:01:36.350 --> 00:01:37.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Enough games.</b></Default>

c0000043
00:01:37.850 --> 00:01:40.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Do you know
Schwartz's whereabouts?</b></Default>

c0000044
00:01:40.310 --> 00:01:41.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Not I.</b></Default>

c0000045
00:01:41.810 --> 00:01:44.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Although, I suggest
you go and retrieve</b></Default>

c0000046
00:01:44.480 --> 00:01:46.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>our sweet little Sisbell
while you still can.</b></Default>

c0000047
00:01:46.900 --> 00:01:48.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-[gasps]
-Understood.</b></Default>

c0000048
00:01:48.780 --> 00:01:50.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And who should
we entrust with this?</b></Default>

c0000049
00:01:50.940 --> 00:01:52.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[giggles]</b></Default>

c0000050
00:01:52.200 --> 00:01:54.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why, you're staring
right at her!</b></Default>

c0000051
00:01:54.700 --> 00:01:55.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'd be honored.</b></Default>

c0000052
00:01:56.030 --> 00:01:58.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To go to the rescue
of my darling sister.</b></Default>

c0000053
00:01:58.830 --> 00:02:00.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please?</b></Default>

c0000054
00:03:30.000 --> 00:03:31.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000055
00:03:39.800 --> 00:03:41.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Pretty sure
it's from the stress.</b></Default>

c0000056
00:03:41.810 --> 00:03:42.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MISMIS]
We thought we were safe</b></Default>

c0000057
00:03:42.930 --> 00:03:44.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>after defeating Vichyssoise.</b></Default>

c0000058
00:03:44.640 --> 00:03:46.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But then, before we knew it.</b></Default>

c0000059
00:03:46.600 --> 00:03:48.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We received word
that poor Mr. Schwartz</b></Default>

c0000060
00:03:48.600 --> 00:03:49.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>had gone missing.</b></Default>

c0000061
00:03:50.020 --> 00:03:51.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[JHIN] The old geezer
was supposed to confer</b></Default>

c0000062
00:03:51.730 --> 00:03:52.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with the Queen,</b></Default>

c0000063
00:03:52.860 --> 00:03:54.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>not to mention provide us
with a safe route.</b></Default>

c0000064
00:03:55.860 --> 00:03:57.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Seems that plan
has been thwarted.</b></Default>

c0000065
00:03:57.610 --> 00:03:59.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're back to square one.</b></Default>

c0000066
00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:00.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[door opens]</b></Default>

c0000067
00:04:00.370 --> 00:04:01.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000068
00:04:01.830 --> 00:04:03.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
No, Sisbell!</b></Default>

c0000069
00:04:04.040 --> 00:04:05.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must get some rest!</b></Default>

c0000070
00:04:05.450 --> 00:04:07.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
This is no time to sleep.</b></Default>

c0000071
00:04:07.960 --> 00:04:08.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm wide awake...</b></Default>

c0000072
00:04:09.040 --> 00:04:10.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunts]</b></Default>

c0000073
00:04:11.290 --> 00:04:14.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I-I cannot believe
they went after Schwartz.</b></Default>

c0000074
00:04:14.130 --> 00:04:15.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It is just despicable.</b></Default>

c0000075
00:04:15.920 --> 00:04:17.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000076
00:04:17.470 --> 00:04:19.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000077
00:04:19.550 --> 00:04:21.600 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
I must return to the palace.</b></Default>

c0000078
00:04:21.680 --> 00:04:23.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There's no time to waste.</b></Default>

c0000079
00:04:23.180 --> 00:04:24.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You can't!</b></Default>

c0000080
00:04:24.430 --> 00:04:26.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You're still sick with a fever!</b></Default>

c0000081
00:04:26.600 --> 00:04:29.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must find out who's
responsible for all of this.</b></Default>

c0000082
00:04:29.600 --> 00:04:31.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
I understand your motivation.</b></Default>

c0000083
00:04:31.690 --> 00:04:32.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>But, please...</b></Default>

c0000084
00:04:32.900 --> 00:04:34.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm asking you to trust us.</b></Default>

c0000085
00:04:35.070 --> 00:04:37.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I swear,
we'll take you home soon.</b></Default>

c0000086
00:04:37.360 --> 00:04:39.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We're close, right?</b></Default>

c0000087
00:04:39.360 --> 00:04:40.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Very close.</b></Default>

c0000088
00:04:40.950 --> 00:04:42.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
There you go.</b></Default>

c0000089
00:04:42.200 --> 00:04:44.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>For now,
please tend to your health.</b></Default>

c0000090
00:04:44.490 --> 00:04:46.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You haven't eaten once
since yesterday.</b></Default>

c0000091
00:04:46.700 --> 00:04:48.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We'll go
once you're strong again,</b></Default>

c0000092
00:04:48.540 --> 00:04:50.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and eating like normal.</b></Default>

c0000093
00:04:50.290 --> 00:04:52.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm grateful for your concern.</b></Default>

c0000094
00:04:52.710 --> 00:04:55.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
I shall have a bite.</b></Default>

c0000095
00:04:55.670 --> 00:04:57.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What sounds appetizing?</b></Default>

c0000096
00:04:57.670 --> 00:05:01.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A warm meal that's easy to eat,
and gentle on a weakened body.</b></Default>

c0000097
00:05:01.890 --> 00:05:04.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Easy to digest,
but full of nutrients.</b></Default>

c0000098
00:05:04.300 --> 00:05:07.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Simple yet rich,
and most flavorful.</b></Default>

c0000099
00:05:07.430 --> 00:05:08.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose
I could manage something</b></Default>

c0000100
00:05:08.930 --> 00:05:10.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>fitting that description.</b></Default>

c0000101
00:05:10.890 --> 00:05:12.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's a very tall order!</b></Default>

c0000102
00:05:12.350 --> 00:05:13.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[awkward laugh]</b></Default>

c0000103
00:05:21.570 --> 00:05:22.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000104
00:05:24.320 --> 00:05:26.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] This one
is from a full year ago.</b></Default>

c0000105
00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:30.000 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I snapped
this one just now.</b></Default>

c0000106
00:05:30.080 --> 00:05:31.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How?</b></Default>

c0000107
00:05:31.250 --> 00:05:33.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How haven't I grown
a single inch?</b></Default>

c0000108
00:05:33.630 --> 00:05:36.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Never mind Lady Alice,
if growth keeps to this rate,</b></Default>

c0000109
00:05:36.250 --> 00:05:38.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>even Lady Sisbell
is on track to outpace me!</b></Default>

c0000110
00:05:38.960 --> 00:05:40.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Why must I suffer so?</b></Default>

c0000111
00:05:42.970 --> 00:05:44.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[groaning]</b></Default>

c0000112
00:05:45.510 --> 00:05:47.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[paper crinkling]</b></Default>

c0000113
00:05:47.640 --> 00:05:48.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No.</b></Default>

c0000114
00:05:48.720 --> 00:05:51.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I can't do such an
embarrassing exercise, right?</b></Default>

c0000115
00:05:52.060 --> 00:05:53.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must. Hmph!</b></Default>

c0000116
00:05:54.060 --> 00:05:56.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>In pursuit of my dearest wish!</b></Default>

c0000117
00:05:57.650 --> 00:05:58.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

c0000118
00:05:58.980 --> 00:06:00.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000119
00:06:00.400 --> 00:06:01.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes, Lady Alice?</b></Default>

c0000120
00:06:01.950 --> 00:06:02.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Rin?</b></Default>

c0000121
00:06:03.030 --> 00:06:05.820 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]
Just the Imperial swordsman.</b></Default>

c0000122
00:06:05.910 --> 00:06:08.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You went from hot
to cold in a split second.</b></Default>

c0000123
00:06:08.290 --> 00:06:09.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] What do you want?</b></Default>

c0000124
00:06:09.580 --> 00:06:11.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm doing something important.</b></Default>

c0000125
00:06:11.410 --> 00:06:12.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
Is that so?</b></Default>

c0000126
00:06:12.750 --> 00:06:15.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't forget,
you told me to check in.</b></Default>

c0000127
00:06:15.710 --> 00:06:17.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What gives?
Are you on assignment?</b></Default>

c0000128
00:06:18.710 --> 00:06:20.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's one way to put it, sure.</b></Default>

c0000129
00:06:21.220 --> 00:06:22.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] I'm on a mission.</b></Default>

c0000130
00:06:22.590 --> 00:06:25.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And I fear failure is not
an option for this one.</b></Default>

c0000131
00:06:25.180 --> 00:06:26.800 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[milk trickling]</b></Default>

c0000132
00:06:26.890 --> 00:06:28.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000133
00:06:28.600 --> 00:06:31.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] I can
hear her mixing something.</b></Default>

c0000134
00:06:31.480 --> 00:06:33.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin, what chemicals
are you mixing?</b></Default>

c0000135
00:06:34.020 --> 00:06:35.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
That's for me to know.</b></Default>

c0000136
00:06:35.650 --> 00:06:38.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This is a secret concoction
that no one can find out about</b></Default>

c0000137
00:06:38.570 --> 00:06:40.320 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>on pain of death.</b></Default>

c0000138
00:06:40.400 --> 00:06:44.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When I'm done, mine will be
as devastating as Lady Alice's</b></Default>

c0000139
00:06:44.320 --> 00:06:45.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and cause everyone in the world</b></Default>

c0000140
00:06:45.530 --> 00:06:47.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to tremble before me!</b></Default>

c0000141
00:06:47.490 --> 00:06:48.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Devastating?</b></Default>

c0000142
00:06:48.870 --> 00:06:49.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it a bomb?</b></Default>

c0000143
00:06:49.950 --> 00:06:51.160 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
I should achieve my goal</b></Default>

c0000144
00:06:51.250 --> 00:06:53.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>in as soon as 30 days.</b></Default>

c0000145
00:06:53.160 --> 00:06:54.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must be bluffing!</b></Default>

c0000146
00:06:54.710 --> 00:06:57.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Not just one!
I'm talking both of them!</b></Default>

c0000147
00:06:57.500 --> 00:06:59.710 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Wait, Rin!
Please listen to reason!</b></Default>

c0000148
00:06:59.800 --> 00:07:01.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That kind of power's
too dangerous!</b></Default>

c0000149
00:07:01.670 --> 00:07:03.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You think I don't
know that already?</b></Default>

c0000150
00:07:03.920 --> 00:07:05.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
But I wanna be huge.</b></Default>

c0000151
00:07:05.430 --> 00:07:07.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanna be like Lady Alice.</b></Default>

c0000152
00:07:07.930 --> 00:07:11.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Huge?
I suppose she means "great."</b></Default>

c0000153
00:07:11.140 --> 00:07:12.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I understand.</b></Default>

c0000154
00:07:12.430 --> 00:07:14.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Alice is truly
something special.</b></Default>

c0000155
00:07:14.730 --> 00:07:15.980 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
I know, right?</b></Default>

c0000156
00:07:16.060 --> 00:07:18.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>As a perfect servant,
I must follow her lead.</b></Default>

c0000157
00:07:18.940 --> 00:07:21.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I have no other choice
in the matter.</b></Default>

c0000158
00:07:21.150 --> 00:07:22.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's not true.</b></Default>

c0000159
00:07:22.610 --> 00:07:23.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here's why.</b></Default>

c0000160
00:07:24.070 --> 00:07:27.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA] Alice values you
just the way you are.</b></Default>

c0000161
00:07:27.110 --> 00:07:28.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasping breath]</b></Default>

c0000162
00:07:28.870 --> 00:07:32.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Rin, I have
a special gift for you!</b></Default>

c0000163
00:07:32.330 --> 00:07:34.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>See?
It fits you perfectly!</b></Default>

c0000164
00:07:34.910 --> 00:07:36.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN] Lady Alice!</b></Default>

c0000165
00:07:36.460 --> 00:07:40.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll pass this on
as a family heirloom!</b></Default>

c0000166
00:07:40.500 --> 00:07:41.880 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It doesn't matter!</b></Default>

c0000167
00:07:41.960 --> 00:07:43.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've gone too far
to turn back now!</b></Default>

c0000168
00:07:44.010 --> 00:07:45.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't be hasty! Rin!</b></Default>

c0000169
00:07:45.420 --> 00:07:46.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[thudding]</b></Default>

c0000170
00:07:46.510 --> 00:07:47.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000171
00:07:48.010 --> 00:07:50.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I've come to save you
from yourself, um...</b></Default>

c0000172
00:07:50.220 --> 00:07:52.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[breathing heavily]</b></Default>

c0000173
00:07:53.060 --> 00:07:54.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ah?
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000174
00:07:54.430 --> 00:07:56.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You...you...
You stupid swordsman.</b></Default>

c0000175
00:07:56.770 --> 00:07:57.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>How could you?</b></Default>

c0000176
00:07:57.850 --> 00:08:00.230 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I don't see anything
devastating, so...</b></Default>

c0000177
00:08:00.310 --> 00:08:01.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's this all about?</b></Default>

c0000178
00:08:01.690 --> 00:08:02.940 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[whimpering]</b></Default>

c0000179
00:08:03.030 --> 00:08:05.280 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Get out of here!</b></Default>

c0000180
00:08:08.320 --> 00:08:10.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[cutlery clanking]</b></Default>

c0000181
00:08:12.370 --> 00:08:15.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Rin sure can be
weird sometimes.</b></Default>

c0000182
00:08:15.120 --> 00:08:17.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hey, Sisbell,
your food's ready.</b></Default>

c0000183
00:08:18.120 --> 00:08:19.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000184
00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:21.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000185
00:08:21.590 --> 00:08:23.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feel strong enough to walk?</b></Default>

c0000186
00:08:24.000 --> 00:08:27.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Of course. I feel so much
better than I did before.</b></Default>

c0000187
00:08:27.090 --> 00:08:28.180 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000188
00:08:29.260 --> 00:08:30.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000189
00:08:30.800 --> 00:08:32.550 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The agony!</b></Default>

c0000190
00:08:32.640 --> 00:08:34.220 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's wrong?</b></Default>

c0000191
00:08:34.310 --> 00:08:36.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must carry me
to the living room.</b></Default>

c0000192
00:08:36.180 --> 00:08:37.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm, I've got you.</b></Default>

c0000193
00:08:37.730 --> 00:08:39.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000194
00:08:40.350 --> 00:08:41.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]</b></Default>

c0000195
00:08:41.440 --> 00:08:44.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, dear,
is something the matter?</b></Default>

c0000196
00:08:44.270 --> 00:08:45.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ISKA]
No, it's nothing.</b></Default>

c0000197
00:08:45.820 --> 00:08:47.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Mine have
grown larger than Rin's.</b></Default>

c0000198
00:08:47.990 --> 00:08:49.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You must have noticed it.</b></Default>

c0000199
00:08:49.780 --> 00:08:51.450 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sounds like you're
doing better now.</b></Default>

c0000200
00:08:51.530 --> 00:08:53.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[coughing]</b></Default>

c0000201
00:08:53.870 --> 00:08:55.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My throat's on fire!</b></Default>

c0000202
00:08:55.370 --> 00:08:56.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000203
00:08:56.950 --> 00:08:58.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What gives?</b></Default>

c0000204
00:08:58.620 --> 00:09:00.580 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Guess they're all
on guard duty.</b></Default>

c0000205
00:09:00.670 --> 00:09:02.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[sighs]</b></Default>

c0000206
00:09:02.130 --> 00:09:03.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000207
00:09:04.000 --> 00:09:05.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Here, eat up.</b></Default>

c0000208
00:09:05.460 --> 00:09:06.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[grunting]</b></Default>

c0000209
00:09:06.550 --> 00:09:09.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My feeble hands shake
too much to hold a spoon!</b></Default>

c0000210
00:09:09.130 --> 00:09:10.930 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Looks like
you'll have to feed me.</b></Default>

c0000211
00:09:11.010 --> 00:09:13.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your hands were fine
just a moment ago.</b></Default>

c0000212
00:09:13.180 --> 00:09:14.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Feed me, now!</b></Default>

c0000213
00:09:14.560 --> 00:09:16.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Um, if you truly insist.</b></Default>

c0000214
00:09:16.350 --> 00:09:18.020 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000215
00:09:19.100 --> 00:09:20.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[munching]</b></Default>

c0000216
00:09:20.350 --> 00:09:22.860 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hmm.</b></Default>

c0000217
00:09:22.940 --> 00:09:25.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL] Now,
it's time to return the favor.</b></Default>

c0000218
00:09:25.730 --> 00:09:28.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Iska, open real wide for me!</b></Default>

c0000219
00:09:28.150 --> 00:09:30.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I thought you were
too sickly to hold a spoon.</b></Default>

c0000220
00:09:30.280 --> 00:09:32.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hurry up or the tasty soup
will get cold.</b></Default>

c0000221
00:09:32.780 --> 00:09:33.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah?</b></Default>

c0000222
00:09:33.950 --> 00:09:36.290 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Say, "ahhh!"
Say, "ahh!"</b></Default>

c0000223
00:09:36.370 --> 00:09:37.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000224
00:09:37.450 --> 00:09:38.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That is enough!</b></Default>

c0000225
00:09:38.620 --> 00:09:40.620 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Are you trying to get us
both killed or something?</b></Default>

c0000226
00:09:40.710 --> 00:09:42.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Huh?
-Never mind.</b></Default>

c0000227
00:09:42.500 --> 00:09:45.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Just finish your food already.
"Ahh!"</b></Default>

c0000228
00:09:48.960 --> 00:09:53.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Stars of fate, reveal the
past I am destined to see.</b></Default>

c0000229
00:09:53.090 --> 00:09:55.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[gasps]
It's not real this time, right?</b></Default>

c0000230
00:09:55.390 --> 00:09:57.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>This puts the Imperial
holograms to shame.</b></Default>

c0000231
00:09:57.970 --> 00:10:00.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Astral spirit of illumination.</b></Default>

c0000232
00:10:00.430 --> 00:10:01.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
It allows me to witness events</b></Default>

c0000233
00:10:01.940 --> 00:10:03.480 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>from the past like so.</b></Default>

c0000234
00:10:03.560 --> 00:10:06.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However, it can only
reach a limited distance.</b></Default>

c0000235
00:10:08.110 --> 00:10:10.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Then, if we're to uncover
who's behind the explosion,</b></Default>

c0000236
00:10:10.740 --> 00:10:13.660 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>it seems our only option is
to get you back to the palace.</b></Default>

c0000237
00:10:13.740 --> 00:10:14.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right.</b></Default>

c0000238
00:10:14.820 --> 00:10:16.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They must have sent Vichyssoise</b></Default>

c0000239
00:10:16.200 --> 00:10:18.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>because they were
afraid of just that.</b></Default>

c0000240
00:10:18.330 --> 00:10:20.910 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>After all, she is from
the House of Hydra.</b></Default>

c0000241
00:10:21.000 --> 00:10:23.210 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Talisman heads that family.</b></Default>

c0000242
00:10:23.290 --> 00:10:26.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You mean it's possible Hydra
is running the show, now?</b></Default>

c0000243
00:10:26.250 --> 00:10:27.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Yes.</b></Default>

c0000244
00:10:27.710 --> 00:10:28.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[SISBELL]
Remember that as we journey</b></Default>

c0000245
00:10:29.050 --> 00:10:30.380 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the Central Province.</b></Default>

c0000246
00:10:30.460 --> 00:10:32.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000247
00:10:32.590 --> 00:10:34.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Don't let your guard down
around them.</b></Default>

c0000248
00:10:34.970 --> 00:10:36.260 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ELLETEAR]
You sure know how to break</b></Default>

c0000249
00:10:36.350 --> 00:10:38.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>a girl's heart, Mother.</b></Default>

c0000250
00:10:38.430 --> 00:10:41.390 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ordering me to stay
trapped inside like this.</b></Default>

c0000251
00:10:41.480 --> 00:10:43.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted to go get Sisbell.</b></Default>

c0000252
00:10:44.690 --> 00:10:47.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A good thing I'm such
a naughty girl at heart.</b></Default>

c0000253
00:10:47.690 --> 00:10:49.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I get all tingly
when I break an order.</b></Default>

c0000254
00:10:49.980 --> 00:10:52.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Especially when
it's one of yours.</b></Default>

c0000255
00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:54.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Say, Alice.</b></Default>

c0000256
00:10:54.820 --> 00:10:57.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'm well aware that
I told you it was reassuring</b></Default>

c0000257
00:10:57.200 --> 00:10:58.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to have you back home.</b></Default>

c0000258
00:10:58.910 --> 00:11:01.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Even so,
I did not mean to imply</b></Default>

c0000259
00:11:01.200 --> 00:11:02.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you should spend
the night with me.</b></Default>

c0000260
00:11:02.960 --> 00:11:04.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I insist, though.</b></Default>

c0000261
00:11:04.160 --> 00:11:06.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>If the killer dares
come after you again,</b></Default>

c0000262
00:11:06.330 --> 00:11:07.960 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I'll be right here
to protect you.</b></Default>

c0000263
00:11:09.670 --> 00:11:11.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I am most grateful
for your concern.</b></Default>

c0000264
00:11:12.550 --> 00:11:14.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You are so dependable
for your age.</b></Default>

c0000265
00:11:14.760 --> 00:11:16.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Far more than I was.</b></Default>

c0000266
00:11:16.550 --> 00:11:18.010 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>No, that can't be true.</b></Default>

c0000267
00:11:19.100 --> 00:11:20.510 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[footsteps]</b></Default>

c0000268
00:11:20.600 --> 00:11:21.850 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
Is that...</b></Default>

c0000269
00:11:23.640 --> 00:11:26.310 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's difficult to believe
we were ever that close.</b></Default>

c0000270
00:11:26.400 --> 00:11:27.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000271
00:11:27.480 --> 00:11:29.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When's this from?</b></Default>

c0000272
00:11:29.770 --> 00:11:31.400 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That was back from
when I was a member</b></Default>

c0000273
00:11:31.480 --> 00:11:33.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the astral power forces.</b></Default>

c0000274
00:11:33.320 --> 00:11:35.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] I've never seen
a photo of you that young.</b></Default>

c0000275
00:11:35.570 --> 00:11:36.990 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Your princess days.</b></Default>

c0000276
00:11:37.070 --> 00:11:38.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000277
00:11:39.990 --> 00:11:41.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is that Salinger?</b></Default>

c0000278
00:11:41.490 --> 00:11:42.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>With you?</b></Default>

c0000279
00:11:42.790 --> 00:11:45.410 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
The two of us were rivals.</b></Default>

c0000280
00:11:45.500 --> 00:11:47.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The boy I once knew is gone.</b></Default>

c0000281
00:11:47.580 --> 00:11:49.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Replaced by a villain.</b></Default>

c0000282
00:11:49.590 --> 00:11:52.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] Can time really
change someone that much?</b></Default>

c0000283
00:11:52.670 --> 00:11:55.720 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Salinger specialized
in stealing astral spirits.</b></Default>

c0000284
00:11:55.800 --> 00:11:57.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He always wanted to take mine,</b></Default>

c0000285
00:11:57.680 --> 00:12:00.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and I had to battle
most fiercely to prevent him.</b></Default>

c0000286
00:12:00.430 --> 00:12:02.470 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Over and over again.</b></Default>

c0000287
00:12:02.560 --> 00:12:03.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE] I don't get it.</b></Default>

c0000288
00:12:03.850 --> 00:12:06.140 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What stopped you
from arresting him?</b></Default>

c0000289
00:12:06.230 --> 00:12:08.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I suppose it felt like a waste.</b></Default>

c0000290
00:12:08.190 --> 00:12:10.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I just couldn't bring myself
to turn him in.</b></Default>

c0000291
00:12:10.730 --> 00:12:12.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's that mean?</b></Default>

c0000292
00:12:12.230 --> 00:12:14.650 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I wanted someone
I could go all out against.</b></Default>

c0000293
00:12:14.740 --> 00:12:16.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?!</b></Default>

c0000294
00:12:16.110 --> 00:12:17.490 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
He stood his ground, even when</b></Default>

c0000295
00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:19.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I fought with everything I had.</b></Default>

c0000296
00:12:19.660 --> 00:12:23.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He was the strongest and rudest
person I have ever known.</b></Default>

c0000297
00:12:23.450 --> 00:12:25.950 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>A true challenger,
and worthy rival.</b></Default>

c0000298
00:12:27.120 --> 00:12:29.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
We're the same, Mother.</b></Default>

c0000299
00:12:29.880 --> 00:12:32.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I feel the same way.
I want that, too.</b></Default>

c0000300
00:12:33.000 --> 00:12:34.340 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
It was a grievous mistake.</b></Default>

c0000301
00:12:34.420 --> 00:12:35.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-Ah?
-In time,</b></Default>

c0000302
00:12:35.760 --> 00:12:38.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>his thirst for power
swallowed him whole.</b></Default>

c0000303
00:12:38.180 --> 00:12:40.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR] He attacked
the late queen to surpass her.</b></Default>

c0000304
00:12:41.050 --> 00:12:43.430 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I was the one who
apprehended him.</b></Default>

c0000305
00:12:43.510 --> 00:12:47.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We shared a dream
of mastering the astral arts.</b></Default>

c0000306
00:12:47.180 --> 00:12:49.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Our bond somehow
transcended the reality</b></Default>

c0000307
00:12:49.650 --> 00:12:51.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of our positions in life.</b></Default>

c0000308
00:12:51.190 --> 00:12:53.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It was forged
in the flames of battle.</b></Default>

c0000309
00:12:54.900 --> 00:12:57.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>However...in the end...</b></Default>

c0000310
00:12:58.110 --> 00:12:59.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Enough.</b></Default>

c0000311
00:12:59.150 --> 00:13:00.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>That's quite enough.</b></Default>

c0000312
00:13:02.070 --> 00:13:04.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Uh, tell me,
did he say anything?</b></Default>

c0000313
00:13:04.450 --> 00:13:06.500 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>When you saw him
at Alcatroz, I mean.</b></Default>

c0000314
00:13:06.580 --> 00:13:08.080 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
Um, well...</b></Default>

c0000315
00:13:08.160 --> 00:13:09.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[phone ringing]</b></Default>

c0000316
00:13:12.000 --> 00:13:14.130 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
I apologize for the late call.</b></Default>

c0000317
00:13:14.210 --> 00:13:16.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Lady Sisbell has left
on the night train</b></Default>

c0000318
00:13:16.130 --> 00:13:18.050 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>headed to the Central Province.</b></Default>

c0000319
00:13:18.130 --> 00:13:21.760 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The train will arrive at its
destination tomorrow morning.</b></Default>

c0000320
00:13:21.840 --> 00:13:24.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MILLAVAIR]
Rin, thank you for the report.</b></Default>

c0000321
00:13:24.180 --> 00:13:25.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I will send Warvick.</b></Default>

c0000322
00:13:25.970 --> 00:13:27.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And Kisasage as well.</b></Default>

c0000323
00:13:27.890 --> 00:13:29.810 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They will meet you at Gate 4.</b></Default>

c0000324
00:13:29.890 --> 00:13:31.690 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RIN]
Understood.</b></Default>

c0000325
00:13:31.770 --> 00:13:34.060 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Sisbell will be with us soon.</b></Default>

c0000326
00:13:34.150 --> 00:13:36.570 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>We will finally be able
to put this case to rest.</b></Default>

c0000327
00:13:38.070 --> 00:13:39.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[ALICE]
I wonder...</b></Default>

c0000328
00:13:39.440 --> 00:13:40.740 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Is it that simple?</b></Default>

c0000329
00:13:40.820 --> 00:13:42.780 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[train horn blowing]</b></Default>

c0000330
