c0000495
00:19:46.230 --> 00:19:48.270 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>you shall sit upon this throne,</b></Default>

c0000496
00:19:48.360 --> 00:19:51.360 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and take my place
as the queen of this hall.</b></Default>

c0000497
00:19:51.530 --> 00:19:53.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?</b></Default>

c0000498
00:19:55.360 --> 00:19:56.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Take heed.</b></Default>

c0000499
00:19:56.950 --> 00:20:00.240 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Sovereignty is in chaos
from the assassination attempt.</b></Default>

c0000500
00:20:00.330 --> 00:20:03.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Queen narrowly survived.</b></Default>

c0000501
00:20:03.330 --> 00:20:05.330 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A] Your
mission is to take advantage</b></Default>

c0000502
00:20:05.410 --> 00:20:08.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of this fragile time
and ambush the Nebulis Palace.</b></Default>

c0000503
00:20:10.290 --> 00:20:12.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My, this is splendid!</b></Default>

c0000504
00:20:12.710 --> 00:20:14.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>To join an astral power trial,</b></Default>

c0000505
00:20:14.720 --> 00:20:17.590 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>I must truly be
a lucky individual!</b></Default>

c0000506
00:20:17.680 --> 00:20:20.300 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Huh?
Where's Director Magnacasa?</b></Default>

c0000507
00:20:20.390 --> 00:20:23.520 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>He's the operational commander
back at the Empire.</b></Default>

c0000508
00:20:23.600 --> 00:20:25.770 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you're raising your voice
way too much.</b></Default>

c0000509
00:20:25.850 --> 00:20:27.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Please try to keep it down.</b></Default>

c0000510
00:20:27.520 --> 00:20:29.440 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>My sincere apology!</b></Default>

c0000511
00:20:30.650 --> 00:20:31.730 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NEWTON]
Let's see.</b></Default>

c0000512
00:20:31.820 --> 00:20:33.900 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Ah, yes, Mei and Nameless</b></Default>

c0000513
00:20:33.980 --> 00:20:37.110 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>should already be in the
Central Province by now.</b></Default>

c0000514
00:20:37.200 --> 00:20:38.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[FEMALE GREAT APOSTLE 11A]
The royal palace consists</b></Default>

c0000515
00:20:38.780 --> 00:20:40.030 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of four areas.</b></Default>

c0000516
00:20:40.120 --> 00:20:43.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Queen's palace, with Lou,
Zoa, and Hydra</b></Default>

c0000517
00:20:43.870 --> 00:20:45.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>forming a perimeter around it.</b></Default>

c0000518
00:20:45.910 --> 00:20:47.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1C]
You will get into position</b></Default>

c0000519
00:20:47.210 --> 00:20:49.830 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>without delay once you arrive
at the Central Province.</b></Default>

c0000520
00:20:49.920 --> 00:20:51.790 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000521
00:20:51.880 --> 00:20:53.920 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS]
Our main target is the Queen,</b></Default>

c0000522
00:20:54.000 --> 00:20:57.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>but we'll likely engage
other purebloods along the way.</b></Default>

c0000523
00:20:57.510 --> 00:20:59.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI] We'll hunt down
every last one of them.</b></Default>

c0000524
00:20:59.760 --> 00:21:02.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's been way too long
since we last worked together!</b></Default>

c0000525
00:21:02.760 --> 00:21:04.100 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Right, Nameless?</b></Default>

c0000526
00:21:04.180 --> 00:21:05.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000527
00:21:05.770 --> 00:21:07.890 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>What's more fun
than a big ol' witch hunt?</b></Default>

c0000528
00:21:07.980 --> 00:21:10.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>♪</b></Default>

c0000529
00:21:10.650 --> 00:21:13.070 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[NAMELESS] Our Class A
target is the Queen.</b></Default>

c0000530
00:21:13.150 --> 00:21:16.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Class B is Zoa's family head,
Growley.</b></Default>

c0000531
00:21:16.360 --> 00:21:18.530 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Class C is Kissing Zoa,</b></Default>

c0000532
00:21:18.610 --> 00:21:21.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and Ice Calamity
Witch Aliceliese.</b></Default>

c0000533
00:21:22.320 --> 00:21:23.370 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Whaddya know?</b></Default>

c0000534
00:21:23.450 --> 00:21:27.040 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Only the House of Hydra
is off-limits this go round.</b></Default>

c0000535
00:21:27.120 --> 00:21:28.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[laughs]</b></Default>

c0000536
00:21:28.330 --> 00:21:29.870 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>It's crystal clear
who's connected</b></Default>

c0000537
00:21:29.960 --> 00:21:31.460 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>to the Eight Great Apostles.</b></Default>

c0000538
00:21:32.840 --> 00:21:34.750 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Oh, we're here.</b></Default>

c0000539
00:21:34.840 --> 00:21:36.670 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MEI]
The Nebulis Palace.</b></Default>

c0000540
00:21:36.760 --> 00:21:39.420 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Their fancy
impregnable fortress,</b></Default>

c0000541
00:21:39.510 --> 00:21:42.090 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>and absolute line of defense.</b></Default>

c0000542
00:21:42.180 --> 00:21:45.970 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now we get to decide
how we want to make it crumble.</b></Default>

c0000543
00:21:46.390 --> 00:21:47.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[MALE GREAT APOSTLE 1A]
Show us the real power</b></Default>

c0000544
00:21:47.770 --> 00:21:49.560 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>of the Saint Disciples.</b></Default>

c0000545
00:21:49.640 --> 00:21:52.150 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Capture the Queen,
and end this war</b></Default>

c0000546
00:21:52.230 --> 00:21:54.610 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>with a triumphant victory
for the Empire!</b></Default>

c0000547
00:21:56.820 --> 00:21:58.190 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>[RISYA]
All units have successfully</b></Default>

c0000548
00:21:58.280 --> 00:21:59.700 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>crossed the border.</b></Default>

c0000549
00:21:59.780 --> 00:22:01.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>They will arrive by tomorrow.</b></Default>

c0000550
00:22:02.160 --> 00:22:04.120 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Hm?
Um, Johaim.</b></Default>

c0000551
00:22:04.200 --> 00:22:07.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You seem oddly comfortable
in the Sovereignty's clothing.</b></Default>

c0000552
00:22:07.620 --> 00:22:09.200 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Think so?</b></Default>

c0000553
00:22:09.290 --> 00:22:11.540 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>You realize we're going
after the Queen herself.</b></Default>

c0000554
00:22:11.620 --> 00:22:14.250 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>Now is the time
to exercise caution.</b></Default>

c0000555
00:22:14.330 --> 00:22:16.170 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>There are some rumors
going around...</b></Default>

c0000556
00:22:16.250 --> 00:22:18.840 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>that the Ice Calamity Witch
is stationed at her side.</b></Default>

c0000557
00:22:19.760 --> 00:22:21.630 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>-She's not.
-Huh?</b></Default>

c0000558
00:22:21.720 --> 00:22:24.680 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The witch is leaving
the palace even now.</b></Default>

c0000559
00:22:24.760 --> 00:22:26.640 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>And you know what that means.</b></Default>

c0000560
00:22:26.720 --> 00:22:28.350 line:90% align:center
<Default><b>The Queen is on her own.</b></Default>

